dct_alternative_sm: Litao Bay to Chu Tao including Weihaiwei Harbor
dct_description_sm: From British surveys between 1898 and 1903 ; published Feb., 1916, at the Hydrographic Office, under the authority of the Secretary of the Navy.
Depths shown by soundings; relief by form lines and spot heights.
"Direction and Rate of Tidal Streams" table, tide note.
Shows shoals, reefs, islands, currents, vegetation, drainage, towns, roads.
